results.name: Second-order linear recurrence sequence with a(n) = a(n-1) + a(n-2).
comment: a(0) = 62638280004239857, a(1) = 49463435743205655. This is a second-order linear recurrence sequence with a(0) and a(1) coprime that does not contain any primes. It was found by D. E. Knuth in 1990.
